data.description: Don't miss out on this beautiful 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom haven that boasts nearly 3,800 square feet of comfortable living space. Nestled against a serene backdrop of lush woods, this home provides a perfect balance of modern luxury and natural tranquility.  As you step inside, the hardwood floors gracefully flow throughout the main level, creating a seamless and inviting open floor plan. The heart of the home is a spacious, sun-lit living area, perfect for gathering with loved ones and hosting memorable gatherings.  The master bedroom offers a true retreat, featuring a vaulted ceiling and a spa-like master bath that's sure to pamper your senses. Indulge in the dual body-jet shower, complete with rainfall shower heads and wands, or unwind in the deep, jetted soaking tub. You'll also appreciate the heated floors, dual sink vanity, and a separate makeup vanity that add a touch of opulence to your daily routine.  Step outside onto the deck, a peaceful oasis where you can enjoy your morning coffee or entertain under the open sky. The fully finished walkout basement offers the ideal space for recreation, featuring a wet bar and an additional full bath for ultimate convenience. Plus, a 2-car front loading garage ensures your vehicles and storage needs are well taken care of.  Situated in a prime location, this home is not only a serene retreat but also conveniently close to shopping and just minutes away from I-66, making your daily commute a breeze.
